
# Archon Integration Rules for FibreFlow_React
# Project ID: fibreflow-react

Before starting any task:
1. Check Archon tasks: archon:manage_task(action="list", project_id="fibreflow-react")
2. Search knowledge: archon:perform_rag_query(query="[relevant topic]")
3. Find examples: archon:search_code_examples(query="[pattern]")

Always update task status when starting work:
archon:manage_task(action="update", task_id="[task_id]", update_fields={"status": "doing"})

Document learnings in Archon knowledge base when discovering new patterns.
